HEADWORD: Unlovely
<hw>Un*love"ly</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Not lovely; not
amiable; possessing qualities that excite dislike; disagreeable;
displeasing; unpleasant.</def> -- <wordforms><wf>Un*love"li*ness</wf>
<pr>(#)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unluckily</ent>⟦br⟧
